{"tid":1180012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"二手市場冰封 先達有手機店拒收華為手機！","createTime":"2019-05-31T13:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T14:03:39.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f120dd8dd787fe93f88aec5a4e9d17e2b591e58a","tid":1180012,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"【華為危機】直擊！先達二手市場冰封 旺角維修中心湧死機苦主｜壹週刊<br />\n<br />\n華為先是被美國封殺，近日又出現「死機」事故。有手機店店主表示，華為手機的二手回收價因而受影響下跌，部份更是暫時停止回收。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前日（29日），大批華為用家的手機疑因系統更新問題而集體死機，各苦主紛紛湧至客戶服務中心修理無法使用的電話。受影響用家殷先生表示，他因把手機設定了自動更新而「中招」，當日一起床便看到手機畫面一片白色，按鍵亦沒有反應。他認為難以救回手機內的資料，故不欲浪費時間，決定選擇較快的修理方法，即重設系統，但對因而失去的相片感到可惜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先達店主Marco指，最近有關華為的新聞不斷，加上近日疑因系統更新問題現「死機潮」，使華為手機的回收價受到影響而有所降低。「華為有個機款叫P20 Pro，在未出事前大約收2000至2200元，現在的回收價因為出事，有明顯的跌落，大約跌至1300至1400元。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除了回收價下跌，有些手機店甚至暫時停止收機。先達店員阿霜便表示，現時情況尚未穩定，仍有待觀察，故暫時不會回收華為二手機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一位先達店主肥老闆雖認為現時的二手市場尚算可以，但認同華為手機的回收價有所下跌，有些店亦不敢回收。「最主要是怕若貿易戰再升溫，不知情況會如何。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他續指，不但放機的人不多，連問價的人也少了。「因為如果回收價不好，別人就不會放，個個也先看清楚情況。無緣無故收少幾百，例如平時收四千多元，現在突然收三千多，你怎會放呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_672817_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_672817_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=7165f0f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_672817_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=0a96ff5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_672817_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"2553e703d61e5b245d295e32767650e7e19ce122","tid":1180012,"uid":163783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"求p30 pro 1000蚊收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1322f81c07ecdde7d28493614030d282c173ca","tid":1180012,"uid":54264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:38:52.000Z","msg":"先達班美帝走狗睇唔起我地華為呀"},{"pid":"fcfa91242e62b39c3f15d786eb897272073eed0f","tid":1180012,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好心涼</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15246e253e74e5f5b5128755d8afd1c742e42c70","tid":1180012,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"咁唔愛國 全部引導去支那"},{"pid":"7c1ea4b87a081b82f1d6a13eb41e83262d8351cc","tid":1180012,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2553e703d61e5b245d295e32767650e7e19ce122","tid":1180012,"uid":163783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"求p30 pro 1000蚊收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"長期飛行模式for影相？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}